message_text:
I had a most nerve-racking series of events.
I was trying different combinations of the material found here but I quickly realized that I had blocked off any possibility of progressing to the next gateway.
In my panic, I slipped on the smooth tile causing me to fall down into the abyss.
I closed my eyes, bracing for whatever was about to come, but it never came.
Upon opening my eyes, it revealed that everything, including myself, had been put back in its original place when I first entered this area.
Unsure what to make of this, but I am now able to continue onwards.
name: level_14
